welcome to ad: an adaptable text editor.

    - https://github.com/sminez/ad

    - you can get set up by cloning the repo and running the following commands:
      - cargo install --path .
      - make setup-dotfiles

    - currently you will required the `9p` tool in order to run the `Slide` command
      for following this tour (and many of the helper scripts provided in the repo).
      It can be obtained as part of plan9port here: https://github.com/9fans/plan9port/

    - from there you can run this presentation yourself by opening the docs/tour directory
      within ad and middle clicking the word "Slide" below or placing the cursor on
      it and typing "@".

                            >> Slide <<
